dc_description_s: This point shapefile represents locations of transportation terminals in the United States such as public transport stops, railway stations, metro stations, ferry terminals, and other significant transportation nodes. This layer is part of the 2014 ESRI Data and Maps collection for ArcGIS 10.2. U.S. Transportation Terminals provides the locations of transportation terminals. All transportation terminals are named and show the state and county they reside in. TomTom International and ESRI. (2014). United States Transportation Terminals, 2010-2014. ESRI Available at: http://purl.stanford.edu/bt766kr3656
